---
title: Spring Chicken Pesto Rigatoni with Spinach, Charred Scallions, Almonds, Ricotta & Bacon
description: Think you’ve had every possible combo of chicken and pasta? Spring this decadent dish on your tastebuds for a flavorful surprise! Lemon juice and basil pesto coat rigatoni for a bright base that lets the stars of the meal really shine. Toasted almonds and charred scallions add smoky depth to pasta, then everything’s topped with garlicky chicken, a dollop of lemony ricotta, and a sprinkle of crumbled bacon. Sweet and savory, rich and refreshing—this delightful dinner features your favorite spring flavors in full bloom.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spring-chicken-pesto-rigatoni-50c44557.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/spring-chicken-pesto-rigatoni-624c447ad734d42cde0d5c21-65e65d26.pdf
